.\" $Id$
.It Fl S Ar socket
Specify an alternative socket file.
The following tokens are replaced in the file name specified:
.Pp
.Bl -tag -offset indent -width Ds -compact
.It Cm %h
the machine hostname
.It Cm %n
the basename of executable, i.e.\&
.Nm
.It Cm %%
a literal
.Sq %
character
.El
.Pp
The default is
.\" %PFL_EXPR {
.\"	".Pa $DATA->{sock} ."
.\" }%
